 \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, if we can put together the performances like we did at the last World Cup, then I fancy our chances.\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1628, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the performances\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1567}, {\"ngram\": \"the last World Cup\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1601}, {\"ngram\": \"our chances\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1627}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We just need to build on what we did at the World Cup and even do better.\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1704, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the World Cup\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The difficult part in all these matches is that the window of time in the international break does not allow for a lot of training time.\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1841, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The difficult part\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1723}, {\"ngram\": \"all these matches\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1744}, {\"ngram\": \"the window\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1763}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1771}, {\"ngram\": \"the international break\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1798}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1823}, {\"ngram\": \"training time\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1840}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We will have to use our experience at the World Cup to win these games because we have few days to train.\\\"\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our experience\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1878}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Cup\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1895}, {\"ngram\": \"these games\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"few days\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1939}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NFF announces date for 2024 Federation Cup AFCON 2025: Preliminary round draw out [Full Fixtures] 2026 WAFCON: 'It would not happen for other tournaments' - Super Falcons' Plumptre slams CAF WAFCON 2026: Super Falcons Ajibade 